show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description:
After a devastating accident, Raj Rathod — the only heir of the mighty Rathod International — is left paralyzed, his dreams shattered and his body unresponsive. While the world begins to move on, one person refuses to let go — Maya, his unwavering girlfriend. Bound by love and sheer will, she stands by his side day and night, fighting every storm with a quiet strength that even fate cannot shake.
To afford the mounting cost of Raj's treatment, Maya races across the city — running errands, knocking on every door, and pushing herself far beyond her limits. In a world that mocked her struggle, she remained unshaken. And in the end, it was her unbreakable faith that became the miracle — Raj rises again, not just to live, but to fall at her feet in love, for her honor, and for the glory of the woman who never gave up on him.
